Hi everyone,

I have been having TONS of crashes, mostly when changing scene: going in the airplane hangar or VAB, or launching. I've recently added the following mods:

- MechJeb

- Near Future Construction

- Habitat

- Module manager

- Docking port indicator

However the crashes occur even when using stock only components. I put below a log. Does anyone have an idea what can cause this, and how to solve it? I can't find anything in the log related to the mods, but I'm not an expert in examining these...
